
Bleak House

Make sure you have the gems 'rublique', 'gruff', and either 'json' or 'fjson'.

Run:
  RAILS_ENV=production BLEAK_HOUSE=true INTERVAL=10 ./script/server 
Browse around in your app. Cause requests. Do stuff. Then:
  RAILS_ENV=production rake auto_rublique:analyze
And then look in log/auto_rublique/.

